Bonus options:
    1. Play multiple games at once
            (If the timer ends, the play can start another game and keep the last one running to show off!)
    2. Use your mouse clicks only - no buttons
    3. Animated success and failure on word submits
    4. Collapsible used words container - show or hide it, whichever you prefer!
    5. A game over message is displayed when the game ends